"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.13.9\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.13.9</span> 标题：废丘、土丘、土堆（tell, mound）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：גַּל, נצה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gal (nitsim))</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:25\">2KI 19:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:28\">JOB 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:2\">ISA 25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:26\">ISA 37:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:10\">JER 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:37\">JER 51:37</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מְעִי, מַפָּלָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：m‘i mapalah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:1\">ISA 17:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：עִי</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：‘i)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:1\">PSA 79:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:18\">JER 26:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:6\">MIC 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:12\">MIC 3:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：תֵּל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:17\">DEU 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:28\">JOS 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:13\">JOS 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:18\">JER 30:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:2\">JER 49:2</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0424_tell.jpg\" alt=\"废丘（伯善）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">废丘（伯善） (© Grauesel, CC BY-SA 3.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>废丘是指某地建于多个不同时期的城镇，由于多次被毁和重建而形成的一座小山。圣地有许多个废丘，其中有很多已被挖掘出来，而且已被确认是圣经中提到的古代城镇。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>古代的城镇经常会被战争摧毁，或者在瘟疫、饥荒过后被遗弃；随着时间的推移，城镇中的建筑也会倒塌。新城市往往直接建造在旧城市的废墟上，并不完全清除旧城市的基础和建设。这个在旧建筑上面建造新建筑的过程，逐渐形成了一座人工的山丘或土丘。在圣经的描述中，这些土丘代表着毁坏和衰败。然而，建造在这些土丘上的城镇地势较高，因而更容易防御。</p>\n<p>除了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:13\">JOS 11:13</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:18\">JER 30:18</a> 可能是例外，上面列出的所有词语都含有某种负面的意思，不是仅仅指上面建有城市的土丘，而是指毁灭性活动所导致的一堆废墟。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:2\">JER 49:2</a> ：原文字面意为“它必成为一个荒废的土丘”的分可以译为：“它必成为一座由废墟覆盖的小山”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直译）。有些译本没有保留文中关于高度的元素，译为“它必成为废墟”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 提供了一个很值得借鉴的翻译范例，译为“拉巴必成为一堆瓦砾。”</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
